{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_2","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,260p' __issue_context__.json\"","aggregated_output":"{\n  \"body\": \"\\nGO:1990334   Bfa1-Bub2 complex \\n\\nwould be better called\\nSIN/MEN two-component GAP complex\\n\\nnarrow synonym  Byr4-Cdc16 GAP complex\\nnarrow_synonym  Bfa1-Bub2 complex\\n\\n\\n\\nAlso revise the definition accordingly\\nA protein complex that acts as a two-component GTPase-activating protein for Tem1 GTPase, thus regulating a signal transduction cascade, called the mitotic exit network (MEN), which is required for mitotic exit and cytokinesis. Bub2/Bfa1 keeps Tem1 inactive until the spindle is properly oriented, thus inhibiting MEN activation. PMID:16449187\\n\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7_FP3X\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"ValWood\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent  please change the term label of \\nGO:1990334 Bfa1-Bub2 complex\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-20T09:52:15Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [\n        {\n          \"content\": \"EYES\",\n          \"users\": {\n            \"totalCount\": 1\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31636#issuecomment-4279565783\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7_FQcO\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/24660028429)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-20T09:52:38Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reac